Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Iran sanctions stalled in UN
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040h40p
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 30 Dec 1979
American patience eroding over slow-moving resolution to hostage crisis. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.